        {
            "title": "華購美大豆步伐緩慢 貝森特疑似放寬期限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國財長貝森特似乎延長了此前設定的中國採購美國大豆的最後期限，但由於缺乏對中國的新出口銷售，市場仍對北京能否達到目標持懷疑態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特周三表示，中國正向著在2月底前購買1200萬噸美國大豆的方向邁進。這一時間點晚於白宮上個月的聲明，當時稱中國同意在「2025年最後兩個月」採購這一數量的大豆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及大豆採購進度以及距離年底還有多少時間時，貝森特當時澄清說，目標是「季末，所以我認為應該是2月28日」。。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d4ad462f-fc4d-3fef-8682-c8579630f2fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然延長的幾個月爭取了更多時間，但幾乎沒有跡象表明中國在加快採購。據美國農業部周四的報告，對華大豆出口連續第四日無新增銷售。該機構數據顯示，中國自10月30日以來僅採購了225萬噸大豆。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2UZFEj1PJnsHU2kQitCKvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4853ae8e6a612bdec95372618e2b37cc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大豆期貨周四在漲跌之間波動。大豆在11月中旬觸及逾一年高位後回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「市場仍然理所當然地持懷疑態度，」StoneX風險管理顧問Matt Campbell在報告中稱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Extends China Soy Deadline But Slow Sales Fuel Doubts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%86%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90%E7%B7%A9%E6%85%A2%E5%BC%95%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-164109728.html",
